{"tid":485301,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"匯豐IT部門合約工人被迫放兩周無薪假期","createTime":"2017-12-01T00:33:56.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-01T07:58:17.000Z","uid":19552,"like":6,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":24,"replies":[{"pid":"9d02fbe59db9e2dc494f666efcd1b65bee906dbc","tid":485301,"uid":19552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-01T00:33:56.000Z","msg":"滙豐控股（005）前年公布3年大計節省成本，2017年底限期將至，集團早前通知資訊科技（IT）部門所有合約員工，除個別例子，其他合約員工需於12月15日起硬性規定放兩周無薪假（furlough），待明年1月3日重新上班，盡可能減省成本。<br />\n<br />\n單以香港區計，有內部員工統計，至少有300人需放無薪假，另有合約員工11月底遭提早解約，未知明年會否繼續獲聘。<br />\n<br />\n集團透過內部電郵通知IT部門經理，所有合約員工需要硬性規定放兩周無薪假。集團解釋，主要由於12月11日至明年1月4日系統沒有新改動（change freeze），而且不少員工本來已經申請假期，集團需要當值的人手不多。<br />\n<br />\n電郵提到，上述安排為全球性，除非個別市場有人手短缺問題。集團亦會考慮個別業務風險、對服務影響、緊急支援需要及監管要求等作出豁免，但事先需向上級申請及解釋。集團亦建議合約員工於放假期間帶備電腦等所需工具，以防有突發工作需要。"},{"pid":"33b40dd598c723e62391a15cdbd5262c9fafce03","tid":485301,"uid":19552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-01T00:35:16.000Z","msg":"有內部員工就指，集團系統於12月不作改動是傳統習慣，但今年卻迫合約員工放無薪假，相信是要趕及年底前達到節省成本目標。「放無薪假已是較幸運，起碼明年會續約，有部分則是12月提早解約。」<br />\n<br />\n據該員工統計，年底前迫放無薪假的員工約300人，但已確定續約至明年6月，主要負責手機過數程式PayMe及網上銀行等電子服務。另有個案則是原定今年底完約，但早前接獲通知，合約提早於11月底完結，由於是合約員工，故只需一星期通知。"},{"pid":"51dac0bfb261faf8208b04beca6f6da76d1655cd","tid":485301,"uid":24764,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-01T00:35:29.000Z","msg":"係hsbc做it係咩心態"},{"pid":"1627d2c48331201ce0c9a4eb7291b5001ee5c8cd","tid":485301,"uid":19552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-01T00:38:01.000Z","msg":"IT佬：部門近年無請長工 合約工連食飯都要被分隔<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.finance.appledaily.com/finance/realtime/article/20170410/56543744\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.finance.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20170410%2F56543744&d=tM%2Bj00NxWG6U68T3aQiASwRJEaK469wi7EMLOMkgk88%3D&h=94bcefdc\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.finance.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20170410%2F56543744&h=4f5267fc\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.finance.appledaily.com/finance/realtime/article/20170410/56543744</a>"},{"pid":"3c8362f2d21a2c74b406536f53a5a90b58d38727","tid":485301,"uid":157327,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-01T00:42:39.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>係hsbc做it係咩心態</blockquote><br />\n自願去做狗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8657fbb6ca18396c4e6e3403241e3c021281c4a1","tid":485301,"uid":1082,"like":3,"dislike":2,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-01T00:47:04.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>係hsbc做it係咩心態</blockquote><br />\n自願去做狗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n係攞入場券姐， 當你只要做過一段時間銀行it工，之後就可以係銀行啲it 轉黎轉去，一路轉一路升<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5bffd2aeab9aa27058d39e5ad93c6c2eeb023b82","tid":485301,"uid":51747,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-01T00:47:27.000Z","msg":"香港好似得佢既銀行secon係佢炒你就7日，你炒佢就1個月？<br />\n都唔明點解呢啲咁既合約都可以容許到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e20a72d845e1f9e2d9446bb1006b1030066a7c15","tid":485301,"uid":3876,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-01T00:49:32.000Z","msg":"留名等睇啲it狗放曬假個system俾人hack<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aa46145f60b9ee3107ea798ecb0ef58b0d53c9e3","tid":485301,"uid":116704,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-01T00:51:29.000Z","msg":"政府仲話推創新科技，笑死人"},{"pid":"879e2c9c5107988c1c1c78f6b2234a2d9f8fcdef","tid":485301,"uid":124585,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-01T00:53:47.000Z","msg":"香港做I.T.真十分有前途.<br />\n仲叫人搞創科<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3b5fd2cf76ee3304c5e417807cd9f205aba91fdc","tid":485301